data.description: FIRST TIME HOMEBUYERS?  OR DOWN SIZING?  OR AN INVESTOR LOOKING FOR A GREAT RENTAL? Check out this SINGLE STORY home with 3 bedrooms, a fenced yard & a One Car Garage. The fully furnished kitchen comes complete with a SS REFRIGERATOR and STOVE as well as GRANITE COUNTERS & a BAR COUNTER that faces the FAMILY ROOM. The DINING AREA overlooks the large fenced backyard. And, if you work from home, need an office or study...or simply want an extra room for exercise or a TV room, this home has it! Schedule your viewing TODAY!
